<p><strong>Skills</strong> Perception +3</p>

<p><strong>Challenge</strong> 0 (10 XP)</p>

<p><strong><em>Pack Tactics.</em></strong> The hyena has advantage on an attack roll against a creature if at least one of the hyena’s allies is within 5 ft. of the creature and the ally isn’t incapacitated.</p>

